window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The end is nigh.</b></p> <p>Separated from his friends, Rob has marched deep into the western Deadlands. He draws closer to the Blight with every step. So do the rest of his allies.</p> <p>Very soon, the Deadlands will erupt into a cataclysmic battle to decide the fate of Elatra.</p> <p>The gods. The Blight. Dragon Queen Ragnavi. Riardin's Rangers.</p> <p>Forces are colliding. Only one faction will survive.</p>"; 
